The paper proposes a technique for transferring experience samples in reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also discusses the importance weighting technique, which is commonly used in supervised learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.LO) in the context of reinforcement learning, which are less likely but still relevant categories.
